{"tid":800304,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"法國Uefa成撚日逼害我地多蒙特","createTime":"2018-08-30T17:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T07:45:42.000Z","uid":204475,"like":14,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"3d0a435a8bcbb876d1c8134f50493df4fa0bc386","tid":800304,"uid":204475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:43:48.000Z","msg":"歐洲足協根本幫拜仁逼害多蒙特<br />\n<br />\n13年入決賽被拜狗搶咗Gotze，對我地已經唔撚公平，但Uefa視而不見又唔肯改期，結果搞到我地輸咗<br />\n前季殺入8強，明明隊巴被人炸，都逼我地第二日比賽，又係甘搞到我地輸<br />\n連續幾年抽到皇馬，屆屆都被皇狗黑，上年拉莫斯打排球搞到我地領先唔到，結果輸撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拜狗就年年抽好簽，今年更加離譜，四大聯賽一隊都無<br />\n反而我地要踢死亡之組，對下體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你Uefa根本就係助長霸權，令我地超越吾到拜狗，食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4015a280a66b38ac8075e76ef72beb628033fa8","tid":800304,"uid":5649,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:44:51.000Z","msg":"間接逼害埋曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43df635f709e0c22d0e5ecc7c71d6219a756a171","tid":800304,"uid":204475,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:45:05.000Z","msg":"屎浩克 賀狗都好簽過我地<br />\n屌，諗起都嬲"},{"pid":"5af7c2ea43ddabdb3171bb96b5d54a7506e7d506","tid":800304,"uid":50745,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:45:52.000Z","msg":"你做乜鳩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77788d1f00060415705b908abdfecf49bc746789","tid":800304,"uid":204475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4015a280a66b38ac8075e76ef72beb628033fa8","tid":800304,"uid":5649,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:44:51.000Z","msg":"間接逼害埋曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyT